lead_paragraph: For all of Dan Quinn's background as a defensive specialist, the Atlanta Falcons' second-year coach is fielding an offense about as good as anyone right now.

headline.print_headline: Falcons Offense Keeps Building Steam in 45-32 Win vs. Saints
